item.title: first session with Daeryl Holzer
item.description: 16:53 Tuesday 30 January 2018 JST My homework after my session with Daeryl is to look up hypnotherapy training. She said I cannot finish reading books because I get started reading, remember the rest, and don’t need to read the rest of the book.
